<subSubSection lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="4" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,310,1779,1805]" box="[189,310,1779,1805]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,310,1779,1805]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,310,1779,1805]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Diagnosis</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1399,1825,1993]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
The new subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Constant &amp; Pham, 2016" authorityName="Constant &amp; Pham" authorityYear="2016" box="[418,588,1826,1852]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" status="subgen. nov." subGenus="Maculergithus">
<emphasis box="[418,588,1826,1852]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Maculergithus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[596,745,1825,1852]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" rank="subGenus">subgen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1870" box="[784,900,1826,1852]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[784,900,1826,1852]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Gergithus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is here erected for the species sharing the combination of the following characters:
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1399,1825,1993]" box="[189,559,1896,1922]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">(1) ground colour black-brown;</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1399,1825,1993]" box="[189,998,1931,1958]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">(2) tegmina with numerous yellow spots separated from one another;</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[189,1399,1825,1993]" box="[189,1060,1966,1993]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">(3) frons with a broad yellow transverse band above fronto-clypeal suture;</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1320,267,365]" box="[190,829,267,294]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">(4) mesonotum with yellow spot on each lateral angle;</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1320,267,365]" box="[190,1257,302,329]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">(5) posterior margin of pygofer of male genitalia strongly rounded posterad in lateral view;</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1320,267,365]" box="[190,1320,338,365]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">(6) anal tube elongate, truncate apically and with apicolateral angles projecting posteroventrally.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="4" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,325,403,429]" box="[190,325,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<heading bold="true" box="[190,325,403,429]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[190,325,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Etymology</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1399,450,511]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
The name is formed by the combination of “ 
<emphasis box="[733,854,450,476]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">maculatus</emphasis>
” (adj., Latin) = spotted and “ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Stal" authorityYear="1870" box="[1216,1332,450,476]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1216,1332,450,476]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Gergithus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, the genus to which pertains the new subgenus. It is masculine in gender.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,396,550,576]" box="[190,396,550,576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<heading bold="true" box="[190,396,550,576]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[190,396,550,576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Species included</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1399,597,800]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<taxonomicName authority="Constant &amp; Pham, 2016" authorityName="Constant &amp; Pham" authorityYear="2016" box="[190,689,597,623]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="luteomaculatus" status="subgen. et sp. nov." subGenus="Maculergithus">
<emphasis box="[190,689,597,623]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Gergithus (Maculergithus) luteomaculatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[697,913,597,623]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species">subgen. et sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(
<collectingCountry box="[928,1032,597,623]" name="Vietnam" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
, Tam Dao National Park), 
<taxonomicName authority="Che, Zhang &amp; Wang, 2007" authorityName="Che, Zhang &amp; Wang" authorityYear="2007" box="[190,1014,632,659]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="multipunctatus" subGenus="Maculergithus">
<emphasis box="[190,686,632,658]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Gergithus (Maculergithus) multipunctatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Che Y. &amp; Zhang Y. - L. &amp; Wang Y. - L." box="[695,1014,632,659]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" pagination="611 - 627" refId="ref6111" refString="Che Y. - L, Zhang Y. - L. &amp; Wang Y. - L. 2007. Seven new species and one new record of Gergithus Stal (Hemiptera: Fulgoroidea: Issidae) from China. Proceedings of the Entomological Society of Washington 109 (3): 611 - 627." type="journal article" year="2007">Che, Zhang &amp; Wang, 2007</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry box="[1031,1106,632,658]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1118,1203,632,658]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Hainan</collectingRegion>
Island: Jianfeng Mountain),
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1399,597,800]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<taxonomicName authority="Meng &amp; Wang, 2012" authorityName="Meng &amp; Wang" authorityYear="2012" box="[190,963,702,729]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nonomaculatus" subGenus="Maculergithus">
<emphasis box="[190,696,702,728]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Gergithus (Maculergithus) nonomaculatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Meng R. &amp; Wang Y." box="[707,963,703,729]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" pagination="1 - 18" refId="ref6697" refString="Meng R. &amp; Wang Y. 2012. Two new species of the genus Gergithus Stal (Hemiptera: Fulgoromorpha: Issidae) from China, with a redescription of G. bimaculatus Zhang and Che, and G. tessellatus Matsumura. Zootaxa 3247: 1 - 18." type="journal article" year="2012">Meng &amp; Wang, 2012</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(
<collectingCountry box="[982,1057,702,728]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">China</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1071,1156,702,728]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Hainan</collectingRegion>
Island: Bawangling Mountain),
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[190,1399,597,800]" box="[190,1247,773,800]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<taxonomicName authority="Constant &amp; Pham, 2016" authorityName="Constant &amp; Pham" authorityYear="2016" box="[190,598,773,799]" class="Insecta" family="Issidae" genus="Gergithus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tamdao" status="subgen. et sp. nov." subGenus="Maculergithus">
